title: Test
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Men, and Women.
The line for Men has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 27.46,
and it peaked at 55-64_years with a value of 29.0.
Women mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 27.43,
which peaked at 65-74_years with a value of 28.5.
Overall Men, and Women are gradually increasing,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Men and Women is roughly same at Year 75_years_and_over compared to the Year 16-24_years.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Men and Women occurs at Year 25-34_years and the smallest difference occurs at 16-24_years.
